108
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:45,470
Time for your medicine.

109
00:07:52,150 --> 00:07:53,190
Time for your medicine.

110
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:58,790
Be good.

111
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:00,670
Open your mouth.

112
